<T>__{says gravely:}
<C>__{narrator}
<D>__{the barometer reads twenty seven inches and dropping. strong winds, as you can see, already at twenty two knots.}
<P>__{(checks his watch)}
<D>__{the time is now four thirty five a.m.}
<A>__{the narrator walks quickly out of the shot. the five canoes land on the beach with the tide. sam, suzy, skotak, and the rest of the troop quickly jump out and drag the boats up the shore.}
